salon.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>We are taking extra care to ensure we are sanitising and cleaning between each client in the chairs.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>We have introduced sanitation-stations with hand sanitiser  please use these, as much and as often as you can.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>The toilet facilities will remain available upon request to your stylist.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>We are still committed to your comfort while at The Leading Edge however you will notice we have begun serving our refreshments teas &amp; coffees in disposable cups and we promise we are doing our best to recycle and dispose of these ethically.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>You may also notice that we have removed magazines, again, this is to reduce germ transfer. Please feel free to bring in your own reading materials.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>All our salon stations adhere to the 2 metre social distancing guidelines and movement around the salon is restricted.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>Our team are following government recommendations and will all be isolating if they show flu-like symptoms, so we ask for your patience and understanding if we need to reschedule your appointment.</strong></p>\\n<p><strong>If you are unwell, or have come into contact with someone with COVID-19 in the last 14 days, please reschedule your appointment, even if you do not have any symptoms.<br /></strong></p>\", \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-01 09:46:43','2025-08-01 09:46:46','c6e135d7-38f4-4862-be64-109161df45e6'),(1941,1941,1,'The Leading Edge Covid19 Important Visit Information','important-visit-information','important-visit-information','{\"89d6e74c-311b-4e96-a7f3-56d502e0cc13\": \"<p>In light of the current COVID-19 pandemic, we wanted to give you an update on the changes we are making in the salon to ensure your safety is our main priority.<br /></p>\\n<p>We are closely monitoring the government and industry advice, and have made some changes in how we operate und