\n<p>For example did you know? </p>\\n<p>If you wash your hair with warm water and rinse the conditioner off with a blast of cold water at the end for a smooth finish and to reduce Frizz.</p>\\n<p>Stick to shampoo on your scalp and conditioner on your ends.</p>\\n<p>Try using an old cotton t-shirt for your dry off, its gentler than a cotton towel.</p>\\n<p>Don\'t use heat styling tools until your hair is completely dry (and air dry when you can).</p>\\n<p>Invest in a silk pillowcase.</p>\\n<p>If you have any burning questions drop us an email and will do our best to reply with the right advice.</p>\", \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-01 09:46:46','2025-08-01 09:46:53','bf703562-eb68-4c2d-8edd-915c9e4d3c04'),(2005,2005,1,'Tips & Tricks','tips-tricks','tips-tricks','{\"89d6e74c-311b-4e96-a7f3-56d502e0cc13\": \"<p>Want to know the not-so-secret secrets of the worlds best tressed? As a hairdresser I would MUCH rather empower my clients with the knowledge to keep your hair in tip-to-shape (plus it make my job much easier for your next appointment time)</p>\\n<p>For example did you know? </p>\\n<p>If you wash your hair with warm water and rinse the conditioner off with a blast of cold water at the end for a smooth finish and to reduce Frizz.</p>\\n<p>Stick to shampoo on your scalp and conditioner on your ends.</p>\\n<p>Try using an old cotton t-shirt for your dry off, its gentler than a cotton towel.</p>\\n<p>Don\'t use heat styling tools until your hair is completely dry (and air dry when you can).</p>\\n<p>Invest in a silk pillowcase.</p>\\n<p>If you have any burning questions drop us an email and will do our best to reply with the right advice.</p>\", \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-01 09:46:46','2025-08-01 09:46:46','ab1bede0-cda0-4e3d-8c89-f42f80e09e0c'),(2006,2006,1,'Love Your Pet Day','love-your-pet-day','love-your-pet-day','{\"89d6e74c-311b-4e96-a7f3-56d502e0cc13\": \"<p>HAPPY LOVE YOUR PET DAY! A day to cel