ure well on your way to manifesting whatever you want out of life. A personal favourite for me as I pursue my goals this year is be open to change and the challenges it brings. Whats something you think we deserve to hear every day? Exchange your affirmations in the comments</p>\", \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-01 09:46:47','2025-08-01 09:46:47','f0c02176-3a8c-4df2-996a-ad78323dfde8'),(2038,2038,1,'Breakfast Spark','breakfast-spark','breakfast-spark','{\"89d6e74c-311b-4e96-a7f3-56d502e0cc13\": \"<p>Whats my secret to slaying in the salon? BREAKFAST BABY - because if it doesnt spark joy, theres no way my work will. After spending time away from the scissors in isolation, like many of you Ive rediscovered the beauty of baking (and no, I dont just mean my face). Whether its banana, sourdough or any bread in between, experimenting in the kitchen has made my mornings even brighter. What recipe should I try next, let me know in our contact page.</p>\", \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-01 09:46:47','2025-08-01 09:46:53','5f9b1b38-d6d3-4432-a821-30e9cdfaf2a8'),(2039,2039,1,'Breakfast Spark','breakfast-spark','breakfast-spark','{\"89d6e74c-311b-4e96-a7f3-56d502e0cc13\": \"<p>Whats my secret to slaying in the salon? BREAKFAST BABY - because if it doesnt spark joy, theres no way my work will. After spending time away from the scissors in isolation, like many of you Ive rediscovered the beauty of baking (and no, I dont just mean my face). Whether its banana, sourdough or any bread in between, experimenting in the kitchen has made my mornings even brighter. What recipe should I try next, let me know in our contact page.</p>\", \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-01 09:46:47','2025-08-01 09:46:47','00520dd2-e394-42f1-8df4-270cc82e1336'),(2040,2040,1,'Hairgicians','hairgicians','hairgicians','{\"89d6e74c-311b-4e96-a7f3-56d502e0cc13\": \"<p>Hey hey everyone, its Gary here. The thing I love most abou