hs, we have absorbed ongoing increases in supplier costs without passing them on to you. However, in order to continue providing the quality you expect and deserve, we will be introducing a small price increase from 1st August which is available to see on our website.</p><p>This change allows us to continue investing in the best products, training, and techniques to ensure you always receive excellent results and great value for money.</p><p>We truly appreciate your continued support and understanding. If you have any questions, please dont hesitate to reach out.</p><p>Warm regards,</p><p>Alan Havery   The Leading Edge Hair &amp; Beauty</p>\", \"e3000e7f-1bdf-48db-91cc-30b73a438004\": [2298], \"e7d8d3ad-81d4-4164-b482-db5f8b283dcb\": false}',1,'2025-08-03 10:42:05','2025-08-03 10:42:05','389ad9d9-fa20-42a2-a65b-7c2f5db80107'),(2588,2588,1,'Default',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:10:47','2025-08-03 11:10:47','73ee2cd5-cc83-401b-9e5a-802fba42f945'),(2591,2591,1,'Lauren1',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:20:29','2025-08-03 11:20:29','ee6ac1d5-e482-474b-9f58-ab427b7ee3a3'),(2592,2592,1,'Lauren','lauren',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2591],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi, my name is Lauren,</p><p>With over 12 years of experience  10 of them at The Leading Edge  Lauren brings a wealth of expertise, creativity, and passion to every client she works with. Trained extensively in both cutting and colouring, she continues to refine her craft through advanced industry courses, most recently working alongside renowned stylist Darren Ambrose to master the latest techniques for long and mid-length hair.</p><p>Laurens true passion lies in creating soft, natural-looking colour. Specialising in balayage and freehand techniques, she delivers beautifully blended, low-maintenance results that grow out seamlessly and enhance each clients natural tones. From sun-kissed blondes to dimensional brunettes, Lauren focuses on effortless, lived-in colour that looks fresh long after you leave the salon.</p><p>In addition to her colour expertise, Lauren has a particular flair for crafting bobs and structured, wearable shapes that flatter the face and are easy to style day to day. Her eye for detail ensures every cut is tailored to complement her clients features and lifestyle.</p><p>Known for her friendly, welcoming approach, Lauren loves helping clients feel confident with hair thats stylish, manageable, and perfectly suited to them. Whether youre after a subtle refresh or a polished new look, shell work with you to create hair youll truly love.</p><p> Book with Lauren today for lived-in colour and precision cuts  from seamless balayage to beautifully styled bobs.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-10-04 13:21:59','9d969e1a-f40a-478b-8213-3c91c4a144d7'),(2593,2593,1,'Meet Our Team','meet-our-team','meet-the-team',NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','0533a80e-eb20-4074-903b-97ecd1ad3250'),(2594,2594,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"5794b33a-9aeb-415a-86ac-186366dc9e2a\": \"Meet Our Team\", \"da309fa1-70bd-497e-b18e-08c2f5fcf4ff\": \"The heart and soul of The Leading Edge  our talented professionals dedicated to your beauty journey.\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','ead5e2d2-7af9-4c81-b05c-dab107720d8e'),(2595,2595,1,'Lauren','lauren',NULL,'{\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\": \"<p>Hi, my name is Lauren,</p><p>I have been hairdressing now for 12 years with the past 10 years at The Leading Edge. I spent 3 years training and since then I have attended a number of courses covering colouring and cutting. Most recently I spent the day with Darren Ambrose looking at new techniques and cuts for me to apply to long and mid length hair.</p><p>My real passion lies within my colouring work from either drastic fashion colours through to discreet natural sunkissed colours. I also love working with highlights and have developed my free hand skills to produce beautiful balayage results as subtle or bold as you require.</p><p>If your looking for a change and want to update your look I Iove creating new styles and working with my clients to provide them with the change they are looking for.</p><p>I love meeting new people which is just one of the many things I love about hairdressing and I would welcome the chance to meet you into the salon to provide you with the colour and look of your dreams.</p>\", \"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\": [2591], \"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\": \"Stylist\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','9f0a864a-e441-4727-996d-b25b697d4d50'),(2596,2596,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"4b6e3b3a-86a2-43a7-a238-035fb72d0e71\": \"Our Team Values\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','95226039-32cd-4d99-aef2-9c6a1c1e0d70'),(2597,2597,1,'Continuous Education','continuous-education',NULL,'{\"39291855-d367-4b20-bb2c-744c49a726ca\": \"fa-graduation-cap\", \"b17ef90b-6729-4e8e-90b4-5dd1685325b2\": \"Our team regularly attends workshops, training sessions, and industry events to stay at the forefront of the latest techniques and trends.\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','7910174d-3a2c-44b9-b50c-0c24ff0a84bf'),(2598,2598,1,'Collaboration','collaborative',NULL,'{\"39291855-d367-4b20-bb2c-744c49a726ca\": \"fa-handshake\", \"b17ef90b-6729-4e8e-90b4-5dd1685325b2\": \"We believe in the power of teamwork and often collaborate on client services to ensure the best possible results for every individual.\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','f11e8d61-4b9c-4851-af05-b7c502cd8b45'),(2599,2599,1,'Passion for Service','passion-for-service',NULL,'{\"39291855-d367-4b20-bb2c-744c49a726ca\": \"fa-heart\", \"b17ef90b-6729-4e8e-90b4-5dd1685325b2\": \"Our team members are selected not just for their technical skills, but for their genuine passion for making clients feel beautiful and confident.\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','6bfcfe9a-a969-4ed7-ba54-66cea3f1b922'),(2600,2600,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"0f6396f5-63b5-46c2-a935-ed73bd4971c4\": \"Interested in Joining Our Team?\", \"5e3f4d2d-3e83-45c5-9de0-2efe8769f437\": {\"type\": \"entry\", \"label\": \"View Careers\", \"value\": \"{entry:2@1:url}\"}, \"d3b61915-e231-4081-a649-bb456eed60f6\": \"We\'re always looking for talented and passionate professionals to join The Leading Edge family. If you\'re dedicated to excellence and love what you do, we\'d love to hear from you.\"}',1,'2025-08-03 11:20:36','2025-08-03 11:20:36','6c1aded4-8fb5-495d-900b-52437a59e4ba'),(2604,2604,1,'Chloe',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:11','2025-08-03 11:21:11','16236bab-d41c-46bd-b28a-16126acfb510'),(2605,2605,1,'Dc6472bd dc3c 4a98 a4ae 958a38018ede',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:11','2025-08-03 11:21:11','58f4a517-590c-43ee-8a8c-b283bfda5171'),(2606,2606,1,'Emily Leading Edge Hair and Beauty',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:12','2025-08-03 11:21:12','25bfa995-1145-43b6-9091-1ba056d71860'),(2607,2607,1,'Gary',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:12','2025-08-03 11:21:12','e246f048-a87e-4ccf-8375-7742dccbe685'),(2608,2608,1,'Hall Marissa',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:12','2025-08-03 11:21:12','ca99b805-5c56-4338-b98a-fd7f993f6c3f'),(2609,2609,1,'Hayley',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:13','2025-08-03 11:21:13','29aff7c6-2d1c-4ceb-85a4-0b97b53b8ca3'),(2610,2610,1,'Jayne',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:13','2025-08-03 11:21:13','1e6d53ef-e78e-4a79-a188-e80cea1a6f3f'),(2611,2611,1,'Kellie',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:13','2025-08-03 11:21:13','12895158-b981-4e31-83c6-24abfb14814e'),(2612,2612,1,'Natasha',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:21:13','2025-08-03 11:21:13','108f3869-696d-4b77-a09a-efe7f236c091'),(2615,2615,1,'Stylist','stylist',NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:22:03','2025-08-03 11:22:03','5e219abb-0404-4b1c-a283-fdf5f2e8c8c4'),(2618,2618,1,'Nails','nails',NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:23:29','2025-08-03 11:23:29','1f174611-07cd-4bd1-bcbd-28924d4e8afd'),(2619,2619,1,'Gary','gary',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2607],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Its our great pleasure to welcome Gary to our team in Hyde. He has been given the name of \\\"The Hair Wizzard\\\" by a number of his clients. Gary joins us with a wealth of experience in both Mens and Ladies colouring and cutting techniques. The first thing you will witness is his attention to detail and shear enthusiasm for his trade which is infectious. He works wonders with curly blowdrys and enjoys using his colouring skills to deliver the results you require. Gary also keeps well up to date with all the latest trends / cuts for the guys too. So why not book in and give him a try.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-10-04 13:21:59','d9ae0029-09f8-4636-a178-c542fea0aad4'),(2620,2620,1,'Hair Abigail','abigail',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2254],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi everyone, Abigail here.</p><p>With over a decade of experience in the hairdressing industry, Abigail has become a specialist in creating effortlessly beautiful, low-maintenance colour. Starting her journey at just 14 and qualifying at 18, she has built a reputation for her expertise in balayage techniques and natural-looking colours that grow out seamlessly and keep clients looking fresh between visits.</p><p>Always staying ahead of the latest trends, Abigail invests in continuous training to refine her craft, ensuring every client receives personalised, modern results that suit their lifestyle. Whether its sun-kissed balayage, soft dimensional blondes, or subtle brunettes, her focus is on enhancing natural beauty while keeping the hair healthy and easy to manage.</p><p>Known for her warm, approachable nature, Abigail loves helping clients feel confident with looks that are stylish, wearable, and uniquely theirs.</p><p> Book with Abigail today for effortless colour that looks amazing long after you leave the salon.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-10-04 13:21:59','ed380680-7292-48c5-bdd4-cacc065f0e57'),(2621,2621,1,'Natasha','natasha',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Gel Nail Technician\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2612],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi I am Natasha,</p><p>I am a fully qualified Gel Nail Technician and I am very passionate about producing the best work I can. I enjoy the challenge of customers bringing images in which they want me to replicate.</p><p>A big part of my enjoyment in the job is building relationships and bonding with my clients during their visit whilst I create the desired look.</p><p>I look forward to meeting you and adding you to my growing client base.</p><p>Tasha x</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2618],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-10-04 13:21:59','f80f9b17-0841-453c-b23a-50ecd8bdaccb'),(2622,2622,1,'Meet Our Team','meet-our-team','meet-the-team',NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-08-03 11:23:35','ae9c3de8-56ad-4afa-8de0-db2db12a3fae'),(2623,2623,1,'Gary','gary',NULL,'{\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\": \"<p>Its our great pleasure to welcome Gary to our team in Hyde. He has been given the name of \\\"The Hair Wizzard\\\" by a number of his clients. Gary joins us with a wealth of experience in both Mens and Ladies colouring and cutting techniques. The first thing you will witness is his attention to detail and shear enthusiasm for his trade which is infectious. He works wonders with curly blowdrys and enjoys using his colouring skills to deliver the results you require. Gary also keeps well up to date with all the latest trends / cuts for the guys too. So why not book in and give him a try.</p>\", \"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\": [2607], \"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\": \"Stylist\", \"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\": [2615]}',1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-08-03 11:23:35','a02a71c9-f2fb-4d89-9559-c349d02b266b'),(2624,2624,1,'Abigail','abigail',NULL,'{\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\": \"<p>Hi everyone, Abigail here.</p><p>I have been in the hairdressing industry for over 9 years now. Starting at just 14, I took a 2 day release from school to go to college and learn the trade as a GCSE. I then went on to complete my apprenticeship with The Leading Edge and qualified at 18.</p><p>I am constantly looking for new challenges and wanting to learn new techniques. I will continue training on different courses to develop my skills further. This way I can keep up with new techniques and keep you lovely ladies up to date with the new trends.</p><p>Hairdressing is my passion, I will help you achieve your hair goals and give you the best advice possible on keeping your hair healthy. I look forward to meeting you in the salon soon.</p>\", \"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\": [2254], \"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\": \"Stylist\", \"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\": [2615]}',1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-08-03 11:23:35','64075488-fc9c-4497-9fde-1edd6e2f2d55'),(2625,2625,1,'Natasha','natasha',NULL,'{\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\": \"<p>Hi I am Natasha,</p><p>I am a fully qualified Gel Nail Technician and I am very passionate about producing the best work I can. I enjoy the challenge of customers bringing images in which they want me to replicate.</p><p>A big part of my enjoyment in the job is building relationships and bonding with my clients during their visit whilst I create the desired look.</p><p>I look forward to meeting you and adding you to my growing client base.</p><p>Tasha x</p>\", \"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\": [2612], \"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\": \"Gel Nail Technician\", \"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\": [2618]}',1,'2025-08-03 11:23:35','2025-08-03 11:23:35','39340523-4898-466d-8aa4-2949d605c8a7'),(2632,2632,1,'Hair','hair',NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:27:14','2025-08-03 11:27:14','c311f22f-4a5c-462e-ad13-86b9dfef4097'),(2636,2636,1,'Aesthetics','aesthetics',NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:30:05','2025-08-03 11:30:05','4f993585-116c-4c68-9b8b-4783d8fb847d'),(2638,2638,1,'Beauty','beauty',NULL,NULL,1,'2025-08-03 11:30:48','2025-08-03 11:30:48','248cee77-3cf9-43f0-883d-e1b1dd4ae28c'),(2639,2639,1,'Jayne','jayne',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2610],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Jayne has been working in the Hairdressing industry for 30 years gaining a wealth of knowledge and experience. Jayne has owned her own 2 floor salon in Hazel Grove and has also attended Lancaster University gaining a Degree in Education which then led onto the delivery of level 1,2,3 hairdressing skills to students with both Skills Solutions and then onto The Manchester College where she managed the Hair &amp; Beauty Department.</p><p>Jayne has worked for many years in the Hazel Grove area with A Cut Above and Chris Baker where she helped to open their training school before going on to open her own salon The Hair Company of Hazel Grove. Jayne had over 6 stylists operating over 2 floors trading successfully for over 8 years before moving into the field of training.</p><p>Having worked in the development of new stylists Jayne has always had to keep up to date with all the latest trends in both cutting and colouring and we are so pleased to be able to offer her unique skills and experience to our clients.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-08-03 11:30:55','2025-10-04 13:21:59','57426484-95e2-40ed-8434-70901d8adb45'),(2640,2640,1,'Emily','emily',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2606],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi there! My name is Emily. I am 21 years old and I am fairly new to the hair industry, but never low on passion.</p><p>I am a very bubbly character, and a perfectionist when it comes to my work; whether it be a shaggy-layered 80s styled cut, a fresh new colour, or simply a beautiful bouncy blow - I\'m your girl.</p><p>I currently work with women and children of all hair types including Afro / Caribbean.</p><p>I\'m offering colour, cut and styling services and soon I will be available for bleach work and highlights too!</p><p>I am also wanting to work with Gents later on in my career. My aim is to be a colour specialist and promote alternative styles. I always aim for the highest quality, and use products which i believe will give you the most benefit, leaving your hair silky soft and manageable. I assure you\'ll leave my chair feeling fresh and new!</p><p>I look forward to welcoming you in the salon soon.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-08-03 11:30:55','2025-10-04 13:21:59','9630c9bf-7fbf-46be-8fa5-532f48b5d2d3'),(2641,2641,1,'Hayley','hayley',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2609],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi, I am Hayley and I am looking forward to meeting you in The Leading Edge after previuosly working at Paul Anthony\'s and Harvey Taylor both in Denton.</p><p>I have been in the hairdressing industry for over 40 years completing my level 3 at the outset. In 2011 I was awarded the prestigious Master Craftsman (for services to the hairdressing industry) by The Hairdressing Journal, to which I am very proud of.</p><p>I love all aspects of hairdressing including P