ntly working alongside renowned stylist Darren Ambrose to master the latest techniques for long and mid-length hair.</p><p>Laurens true passion lies in creating soft, natural-looking colour. Specialising in balayage and freehand techniques, she delivers beautifully blended, low-maintenance results that grow out seamlessly and enhance each clients natural tones. From sun-kissed blondes to dimensional brunettes, Lauren focuses on effortless, lived-in colour that looks fresh long after you leave the salon.</p><p>In addition to her colour expertise, Lauren has a particular flair for crafting bobs and structured, wearable shapes that flatter the face and are easy to style day to day. Her eye for detail ensures every cut is tailored to complement her clients features and lifestyle.</p><p>Known for her friendly, welcoming approach, Lauren loves helping clients feel confident with hair thats stylish, manageable, and perfectly suited to them. Whether youre after a subtle refresh or a polished new look, shell work with you to create hair youll truly love.</p><p> Book with Lauren today for lived-in colour and precision cuts  from seamless balayage to beautifully styled bobs.</p>\", \"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\": [2591], \"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\": \"Stylist\", \"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\": true}',1,'2025-09-25 09:17:16','2025-09-25 09:17:16','c876d21d-07f2-43c7-9251-359e455121a6'),(2864,2864,1,'Abigail','abigail',NULL,'{\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\": \"<p>Hi everyone, Abigail here.</p><p>With over a decade of experience in the hairdressing industry, Abigail has become a specialist in creating effortlessly beautiful, low-maintenance colour. Starting her journey at just 14 and qualifying at 18, she has built a reputation for her expertise in balayage techniques and natural-looking colours that grow out seamlessly and keep clients looking fresh between visits.</p><p>Always staying ahead of the latest trends, Abigail invests in conti