 skills to deliver the results you require. Gary also keeps well up to date with all the latest trends / cuts for the guys too. So why not book in and give him a try.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59','b1a3464a-59f7-4d24-a330-6d2fcebc876b'),(3131,3131,1,'Hair Abigail','abigail',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2254],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi everyone, Abigail here.</p><p>With over a decade of experience in the hairdressing industry, Abigail has become a specialist in creating effortlessly beautiful, low-maintenance colour. Starting her journey at just 14 and qualifying at 18, she has built a reputation for her expertise in balayage techniques and natural-looking colours that grow out seamlessly and keep clients looking fresh between visits.</p><p>Always staying ahead of the latest trends, Abigail invests in continuous training to refine her craft, ensuring every client receives personalised, modern results that suit their lifestyle. Whether its sun-kissed balayage, soft dimensional blondes, or subtle brunettes, her focus is on enhancing natural beauty while keeping the hair healthy and easy to manage.</p><p>Known for her warm, approachable nature, Abigail loves helping clients feel confident with looks that are stylish, wearable, and uniquely theirs.</p><p> Book with Abigail today for effortless colour that looks amazing long after you leave the salon.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59','32908189-e6ed-4e4a-84b7-0fcbddf3d7f9'),(3132,3132,1,'Lauren','lauren',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2591],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi, my name is Lauren,</p><p>With over 12 years of experience  10 of them at The Leading Edge  Lauren brings a wealth of expertise, creativity, and passion to every client she works with. Trained extensively in both cutting and colouring, she continues to refine her craft through advanced industry courses, most recently working alongside renowned stylist Darren Ambrose to master the latest techniques for long and mid-length hair.</p><p>Laurens true passion lies in creating soft, natural-looking colour. Specialising in balayage and freehand techniques, she delivers beautifully blended, low-maintenance results that grow out seamlessly and enhance each clients natural tones. From sun-kissed blondes to dimensional brunettes, Lauren focuses on effortless, lived-in colour that looks fresh long after you leave the salon.</p><p>In addition to her colour expertise, Lauren has a particular flair for crafting bobs and structured, wearable shapes that flatter the face and are easy to style day to day. Her eye for detail ensures every cut is tailored to complement her clients features and lifestyle.</p><p>Known for her friendly, welcoming approach, Lauren loves helping clients feel confident with hair thats stylish, manageable, and perfectly suited to them. Whether youre after a subtle refresh or a polished new look, shell work with you to create hair youll truly love.</p><p> Book with Lauren today for lived-in colour and precision cuts  from seamless balayage to beautifully styled bobs.</p>\",\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59','6642a45f-865f-4d76-8536-9fe2ce38237b'),(3133,3133,1,'Jayne','jayne',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2610],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Jayne has been working in the Hairdressing industry for 30 years gaining a wealth of knowledge and experience. Jayne has owned her own 2 floor salon in Hazel Grove and has also attended Lancaster University gaining a Degree in Education which then led onto the delivery of level 1,2,3 hairdressing skills to students with both Skills Solutions and then onto The Manchester College where she managed the Hair &amp; Beauty Department.</p><p>Jayne has worked for many years in the Hazel Grove area with A Cut Above and Chris Baker where she helped to open their training school before going on to open her own salon The Hair Company of Hazel Grove. Jayne had over 6 stylists operating over 2 floors trading successfully for over 8 years before moving into the field of training.</p><p>Having worked in the development of new stylists Jayne has always had to keep up to date with all the latest trends in both cutting and colouring and we are so pleased to be able to offer her unique skills and experience to our clients.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59','3e47f16b-95c7-4932-83d1-ca883fbaac07'),(3134,3134,1,'Emily','emily',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2606],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi there! My name is Emily. I am 21 years old and I am fairly new to the hair industry, but never low on passion.</p><p>I am a very bubbly character, and a perfectionist when it comes to my work; whether it be a shaggy-layered 80s styled cut, a fresh new colour, or simply a beautiful bouncy blow - I\'m your girl.</p><p>I currently work with women and children of all hair types including Afro / Caribbean.</p><p>I\'m offering colour, cut and styling services and soon I will be available for bleach work and highlights too!</p><p>I am also wanting to work with Gents later on in my career. My aim is to be a colour specialist and promote alternative styles. I always aim for the highest quality, and use products which i believe will give you the most benefit, leaving your hair silky soft and manageable. I assure you\'ll leave my chair feeling fresh and new!</p><p>I look forward to welcoming you in the salon soon.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59','4e0c0bd6-3747-4fa5-893f-ce60f8145c6c'),(3135,3135,1,'Chloe','chloe',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Apprentice Hairdresser\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[2604],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi I\'m Chloe. I\'m 18 years old and I have been completing my apprenticeship for the last 18 months. At the moment i\'m available for blowdrys and some root tints and toners. I am completing my course at Tameside college and The Leading Edge.</p><p>I am a friendly, motivated and passionate individual and welcome anyone into the salon and put 100% into all of my work. If anyone is willing to be a model for me in the future don\'t hesitate to give us a ring, I would really appreciate it and i\'ll look forward to meeting you in the salon soon.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2632],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59','6cb6ce06-7140-408e-bf7c-8167647bb60f'),(3136,3136,1,'Kellie','kellie',NULL,'{\"b61bf591-76e4-4068-bd54-cf8a11ed496d\":\"Hair Stylist\",\"a002485b-6b34-4f64-9681-b48ec473cade\":[3117],\"7b604251-5c83-477c-98a3-1148494e0d26\":\"<p>Hi All, I\'m looking forward to working with all the lovely ladies and staff at The Leading Edge Hair Beauty.<br />I have over 30 years experience in the hairdressing industry mainly based in and around the Tameside area. I love making ladies feel fabulous and well looked after offering cuts and colours tailored to your specific requirements. I cant wait to welcome you into the salon and be of service to you. Best wishes Kellie.</p>\",\"fdd05f4f-b125-4094-95a9-8cd20e626ea3\":[2615],\"be51c651-1817-460e-b798-ef154f7722f1\":true}',1,'2025-10-04 13:21:59','2025-10-04 13:21:59',